    "400204": {
        "Desc": "Go to the opera house to identify the culprit",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "It would appear that I must repeat my question again, Mr. Tartaglia."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "Do you accept the charge that you are the true culprit behind the serial disappearances case?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "To be perfectly honest, I don't understand your country's complicated court system, or the reason why I'm being charged with something I've never even heard of."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "However, I did hear that people who have been charged can choose to participate in a duel to clear their name. Is that right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "In which case, as long as I accept the charge, I can have an all-out fight with that Champion Duelist Clorinde, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "I've gotta admit, that's one of the most enticing offers I've ever received."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "When I privately sparred with her last time, she was obviously holding back... Real disappointing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "Hey, don't you understand? You're currently the prime suspect for a major case! This isn't the place for you to be looking for fights."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "Ooh? Sounds like the Hydro Archon wants to lecture me on the ways of the opera house..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "Then why don't you duel me, too? I'm the kind of student that learns best in the heat of battle."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Furina",
                    "T": "A—Ah, no no no, that's not what I meant..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "Alas, it would appear that communication with the defendant is going poorly, and we have made very little progress."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "In that case, let me explain everything from the very beginning again. The goal of this trial is to determine the culprit behind the serial disappearances case..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Navia",
                    "T": "That case had nothing to do with him! You've got the wrong man!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Confident Audience Member",
                    "T": "Huh!? What's going on?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Doubtful Audience Member",
                    "T": "Why is she interjecting again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Contemplative Audience Member",
                    "T": "Hah, I told you it couldn't be one of the Fatui Harbingers!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "Miss Navia, this is the second time you've interrupted the court proceedings. I only tolerated your behavior last time because you were able to provide the court with a key eyewitness."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "But that was an exception rather than standard court protocol. I can very well charge you with contempt of court for your interjections."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Navia",
                    "T": "Please, did you ever think I had any respect for this place's pointless theatrics?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Navia",
                    "T": "We can put that discussion aside for now, I'm not here to argue with you. I'm here to charge the true culprit behind the serial disappearances case."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Navia",
                    "T": "And if my charges prove true, then Tartaglia here will be proven innocent by default, correct?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "Oh? A young lady has charged in and offered to clear my name, how fascinating. Well, I'd gotten half bored to death by all these rules and procedures anyway, so I'll take you up on that offer."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "So, Your Honor, is there nothing else for me to do now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "You may take a seat for now in the audience, but that doesn't mean the suspicions against you have been lifted."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Neuvillette",
                    "T": "Now then, Miss Navia, who is the person you would like to charge instead?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Navia",
                    "T": "That person is..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
